        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrogenation reaction",
        "description": "使用一系列双金属Pt/SAPO-11催化剂（添加La、Ce、Sn、Fe、Co、Ni、Cu、Zn等助剂），在高压微型固定床反应器中对蓖麻油进行一步连续催化加氢处理，制备生物航空煤油（C8-C16烷烃）。评估了催化剂的加氢脱氧性能、C8-C16烷烃选择性、C8-C16异构烷烃选择性和C8-C16芳烃选择性。",
        "text_snippet": "Using castor oil as the model molecular probe, a one-step continuous catalyzed hydrogenation preparation of bio-aviation kerosene was carried out in a high pressure micro fixed-bed reactor. The effects of bimetallic multifunctional catalysts with an auxiliary metal agent on hydrodeoxygenation performance, the selectivity of C8-C16 alkanes, the selectivity of C8-C16 iso-alkanes and the selectivity of C8-C16 arene were evaluated systematically.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
    ]
